#: templates/index.html:31
msgid "index.instructions"
msgstr ""
"<p>If you have lost or found something, tap the <code>+</code> at the top"
" to create a report. <strong>Items you have borrowed shall be marked "
"<code>found</code>.</strong> In case you can't be easily reached by "
"school email, please include contact details in the report "
"description.</p><p>Browse reports to find ones of opposite type matching "
"your item. Alternatively, use one of the two buttons above to view a list"
" of automatically generated report pairs. These are also displayed on the"
" details page of a report.</p><p>Once you have found a report which you "
"believe describes an item your have lost/found/borrowed, message the "
"report author privately (using the contact details from the description, "
"if provided) and arrange for pickup. When the case is resolved, both "
"sides should delete the corresponding reports on their ends.</p>"

